<li>transform 缩放</li>
</ol>
<div class="language-css line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="css" data-title="css"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token selector">.border-1px</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span></span>
