<p>Q: 说说 CSS 预处理器的优势和区别？
A: 常见的预处理器特性：</p>
<div class="language-scss line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="scss" data-title="scss"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token comment">// SCSS 示例</span></span>
